# Purpose: Restricts repository tracking to root docs and Markdown system prompts.
# Usage: Read by Git ignore matching in the repository root.

# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Repository control/documentation files.
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Allow traversal into the system prompt tree.
!System Prompt v2/
!System Prompt v2/**/

# Allow only Markdown files under the system prompt tree.
!System Prompt v2/*.md
!System Prompt v2/**/*.md
!.gitattributes
